{"tid":2515225,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《泰晤士報》調查中港如何「買起」英國　羅列近 200 項交易總值 1.5 萬億港元","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:40:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb6aa76b254d3f9cfee58d227ab5e745952d57f","tid":2515225,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:19:54.000Z","msg":"《泰晤士報》調查中港如何「買起」英國　羅列近 200 項交易總值 1.5 萬億港元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A0%B1-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95-%E8%B2%B7%E8%B5%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E7%BE%85%E5%88%97%E8%BF%91-200-%E9%A0%85%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%B8%BD%E5%80%BC-1-5-%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595-%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25BF%2591-200-%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%2580%25BC-1-5-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=3f6c70a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595-%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25BF%2591-200-%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%2580%25BC-1-5-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%2F&h=490c9deb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A0%B1-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95-%E8%B2%B7%E8%B5%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E7%BE%85%E5%88%97%E8%BF%91-200-%E9%A0%85%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%B8%BD%E5%80%BC-1-5-%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》當地時間今日（2 日）發表調查報道，詳列近 200 項交易，反映中港買家如何大手購入英國資產，包括企業、基建、物業等，總值近 1,350 億英鎊（約 14,488 億港元）。報道形容這些交易是快速 (swift) 而且不為人知 (unnoticed)。近 200 項交易中，超過 80 項是在 2019 年及之後進行，有最少 440 億英鎊（4,722 億港元）產業是由中國國企持有。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n報道指，中國及香港公司或投資者有份持有的英國產業，包括英國核心基建，如泰晤士水務公司 (Thames Water)、英國能源網路 (UK Power Networks) 及希斯路機場 (Heathrow airport)。此外，中國公司或投資者亦持有最少 17 家私立學校，及總值約 100 億英鎊（1,073 億港元）的物業。<br />\n<br />\n惟須注意的是，今次調查涉及的對象，包括由中國或香港購買或投資的產業。比如購入英國能源網路 (UK Power Networks) 的，就是香港首富李嘉誠。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，許多產業的價值是以購買當日計算，而不反映其後價值升跌。報道又表示，由於有數十項投資無法估值，因此實際總值很可能大幅超過 1,350 億英鎊。"},{"pid":"8f561c5b9f782e047cc3b66973c3d2f613415152","tid":2515225,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:34:53.000Z","msg":"成日話英國經濟差脫完歐冇前景d但又瘋狂掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a6b65e38c007aa5d32ff1a9b54c9db60a5ae65","tid":2515225,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f561c5b9f782e047cc3b66973c3d2f613415152","tid":2515225,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:34:53.000Z","msg":"成日話英國經濟差脫完歐冇前景d但又瘋狂掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:37:10.000Z","msg":"唔先唱衰點買野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59672493e8297464cfde76e3ec54da973c440b0","tid":2515225,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:37:18.000Z","msg":"支持誠哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JWWyzwFUL5U/XwcQenoaOQI/AAAAAAAIYoU/DIntmCSCWxYdRBwqWbVoOjWnDoMsmzL0gCPcBGAsYHg/s1600/FB_IMG_1594298428221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https